title.$t: WE DID IT!! - Dark Souls - Part 15

media$description.$t:
Sad to see this journey come to an end bros!
I know many are gonna complain that I didn't do the DLC, but as I explained in the video I really couldn't. I hope in the future I can do it instead!

I'm sorry this series didn't give much attention to the story. It's there for those who pay attention and it's actually pretty interesting. I'm also a little regretful I had to play in offline mode since many of the online aspects seems like a big part of the game as well. 
I do recommend checking this game out for yourself if you're up for a challenge and to better compliment these parts.

Cant thank you bros enough for sticking through this series!

Stay awesome!
